{"tid":2223374,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"一人N套嚇撚到賴屎/高質 嘅 鬼片/恐怖片","createTime":"2020-09-29T19:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T09:15:31.000Z","uid":119994,"like":7,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"6b556fe0f81f63b77a01e5a4b1fe428fd84aaa95","tid":2223374,"uid":119994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T19:14:55.000Z","msg":"嚇撚到賴屎:<br />\nHereditary 祖孽<br />\nThe Witch 不巫之地 / 女巫<br />\n咒怨1+2<br />\nThe Conjuring 詭屋驚凶實錄 1+2<br />\nThe Haunting of Hill House 鬼入侵 (劇)<br />\nMarianne 惡靈瑪麗安 (劇)<br />\n<br />\n唔算賴屎但刺激:<br />\nA Quiet Place 無聲絕境<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高質/有深度:<br />\nMidsommar  仲夏魘<br />\nThe Shining 閃靈<br />\nApostle 使徒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">睇到好難再搵到高質鬼片，大家幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"00a5a0c1692899b3860e51c41ecfdf1a9ddfeb8d","tid":2223374,"uid":333199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T19:16:43.000Z","msg":"無名屍詛咒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9641cae5eba923ccf79ec2cbfd0dc41dbc93ef4a","tid":2223374,"uid":307619,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T19:16:59.000Z","msg":"細個睇嘅嘅大隻佬<br />\n張柏芝個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64484b2918ebb8425dcb54e739222b2065d87711","tid":2223374,"uid":189506,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T19:21:15.000Z","msg":"詭屋驚凶實錄 1+2真心賴屎<br />\n未試過睇一套戲係頂唔順到想佢快啲完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完之後幾個禮拜都唔敢夜返屋企，一到夜晚就好撚驚"},{"pid":"2dc90c1f1b5d5f1292e7ebc4e0c6b94bb92cfe5c","tid":2223374,"uid":295230,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"ci