似唔係好出名,但真實故事改編幾正"},{"pid":"6a970bde65aa45160975154bde377a6b16fffb6d","tid":2223374,"uid":186755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7731b1b4caa66d757e791fd111ea9a3b0ab2ca8e","tid":2223374,"uid":186755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:00:10.000Z","msg":"凌晨三點三<br />\n好似唔係好出名,但真實故事改編幾正"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:02:26.000Z","msg":"靈時三點三"},{"pid":"3369ad7902a40f77c06c235e6d5ebd799eab012a","tid":2223374,"uid":89823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:13:09.000Z","msg":"the witch印象中好似唔係好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4fd0df052e556305098190783f582961f50171","tid":2223374,"uid":82068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:17:24.000Z","msg":"鬼影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a889d3e6fe02793c6604ff7e549c8a7d82512c5","tid":2223374,"uid":130121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:24:44.000Z","msg":"The Conjuring 我覺得第一集都幾恐怖<br />\n反而第2集 氣氛好似差少少咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我印象最深刻係 意大利驅魔實錄<br />\n我覺得依套好恐怖 唔知係咪係我第一套睇嘅驅魔片關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果時睇完套戲 片尾仲有啲真相話 真人真事<br />\n搞到我果幾日都疑神疑鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26dfa779b1fb0111d8a48194a1a694495bb08abf","tid":2223374,"uid":26766,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:25:42.000Z","msg":"熱血青年"},{"pid":"6845abed561c03b991b766406318e4890b8e37c3","tid":2223374,"uid":232754,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:51:48.000Z","msg":"睇到有陰影應該係大頭怪嬰，可能因為好細個睇<br />\n其實都係一路避一路睇最撚記得個怪嬰啲喊聲好似啲老牛聲咁，細個因為呢樣發左好多次惡夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家諗起都起雞皮"},{"pid":"50c505f74f41859ddc680a3dbd4916a19e50e7fa","tid":2223374,"uid":5218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:41:53.000Z","msg":"今猛夜都唔錯。"},{"pid":"b159122ccd5403c3147855828560cfa9fc2aced5","tid":2223374,"uid":119994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f387cd2f2396e5b92402a4e39cb15d1ea5e5162","tid":2223374,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:51:25.000Z","msg":"無圖點討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nI mean 屎呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25be2102887d31bf4f06c79da1d761430209c1c","tid":2223374,"uid":14802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26dfa779b1fb0111d8a48194a1a694495bb08abf","tid":2223374,"uid":26766,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T02:25:42.000Z","msg":"熱血青年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T04:55:06.000Z","msg":"捐血救人 害己害人"},{"pid":"27cf2559307858fae8b5a909fca758a7332a76c5","tid":2223374,"uid":12994,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"64484b2918ebb8425dcb54e739222b2065d87711","tid":2223374,"uid":189506,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T19:21:15.000Z","msg":"詭屋驚凶實錄 1+2真心賴屎<br />\n未試過睇一套戲係頂唔順到想佢快啲完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇完之後幾個禮拜都唔敢夜返屋企，一到夜晚就好撚驚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"呢套戲，我同女友睇<br />\n第一次佢驚，係咁遮眼<br />\n睇完套戲，隔幾日又話睇<br />\n話咩上次驚得滯，遮住左眼睇唔晒全部<br />\n所以想睇多次 心諗屌你咩<br />\n但我其實好撚驚 你知啦 呢兩套戲又勁長<br />\n啲聲又大 真心嚇撚死<br />\n最後又陪佢睇多次 好彩無懶屎懶尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我都遮左眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097cd1c83eafc60309ac315dc10c38b6f6afcf72","tid":2223374,"uid":127033,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":